snippet.title: Cut Me Deeply OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
(GAME IS ARCHIVED AND UNAVAILABLE)

I used Devtober 2021 as an excuse to finally learn RPG Maker VX Ace, its been sitting in my Steam library for so long that its not the newest version of RPG Maker anymore.  Which is also a testimony to my age, I think.

DOWNLOAD ON ITCH.IO: https://sciaenops.itch.io/cut-me-deeply
